org.fhnw.aigs.TicTacToe.client

Class TicTacToeMain

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • org.fhnw.aigs.TicTacToe.client.TicTacToeMain

  • public class TicTacToeMain
extends javafx.application.Application
    main class of the client application.
    All major settings of the particular game, like the game name or the game mode are to be defined in this class.
    Don't forgett to set the same game name in the class GameLogic in the package 'server'.
